  ## See https://github.com/wch/r-source/blob/d4e8fc9832f35f3c63f2201e7a35fbded5b5e14c/src/library/tools/R/QC.R##L1950-L1980
  ## Setting the class is needed to avoid a note about returning the wrong class.
